Package com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter

Class CriteriaFilter.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter.CriteriaFilter.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    CriteriaFilter
    public static class CriteriaFilter.Builder
extends Object
    Inner class used for Building an instance of a CriteriaFilter, following the builder pattern. Use this Builder class to build CriteriaFilters. A CriteriaFilter can produce the following constructs, as examples:

    Example of a CriteriaFilter with a SimpleCriteria: 

                           CriteriaFilter
        ______________________/\______________________
       /                                              \
      /                          CriteriaSet           \
     /            ___________________/\_________________\
    /            /                                      \\
   /            /                 SimpleCriteria         \\
  /            /      __________________/\________________\\
 /            /      /                                    \\\
 ?criteria={"names":[{"firstName":"John","lastName":"Smith"}]}

    Example of a CriteriaFilter with a NamedSimpleCriteria: 

                                                CriteriaFilter
            ______________________________________/\__________________________________
           /                                                                          \
          /                                           CriteriaSet                      \
         /           _____________________________________/\____________________________\
        /           /                                                                   \\
       /           /                                           NamedSimpleCriteria       \\
      /           /                         _________________________/\___________________\\
     /           /                        /                                               \\\
    /           /                        /Name                  SimpleCriteria             \\\
   /           /                        / / \       _____________________/\_________________\\\
  /           /                        / /   \    /                                         \\\\
 ?criteria={"alternativeCredentials": [{"type": {"id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"}}]}

    Example of a CriteriaFilter with SimpleCriteria in multiple CriteriaSets: 

    

                                        CriteriaFilter
        _______________________________________/\__________________________________
       /                                                                           \
      /                        CriteriaSet                             CriteriaSet  \
     /          ___________________/\____________________           _________/\______\
    /          /                                         \         /                  \
   /          /                   SimpleCriteria          \       /     SimpleCriteria\\
  /          /          ________________/\_________________\     /        ______/\_____\\
 /          /          /                                   \\   /       /              \\\
 ?criteria={"names":[{"firstName":"John","lastName":"Smith"}],"roles":[{"role":"student"}]}

      • withCriteriaSet

        public CriteriaFilter.Builder withCriteriaSet​(String criteriaSetName,
                                              String criteriaKey,
                                              String criteriaValue)
        Specifies the criteriaSetName, key, and value used when building a CriteriaFilter. This is a convenience method equivalent to 
        withCriteriaSet( criteriaSetName, new SimpleCriteria(criteriaKey, criteriaValue) );
        Parameters:
        criteriaSetName - The name of the criteriaSet to specify.
        criteriaKey - The key for the SimpleCriteria.
        criteriaValue - The value of the SimpleCriteria.
        Returns:
        this Builder object.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - Thrown if the criteriaKey or criteriaValue are null or blank.

      • withCriteriaSet

        public CriteriaFilter.Builder withCriteriaSet​(String criteriaSetName,
                                              SimpleCriteria simpleCriteria)
        Specifies the criteriaSetName used with the given SimpleCriteria when building a CriteriaFilter.
        Parameters:
        criteriaSetName - The name of the criteriaSet to specify.
        simpleCriteria - A SimpleCriteria associated with current CriteriaSet.
        Returns:
        this Builder object.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - Thrown if the simpleCriteria is null.

      • withSimpleCriteria

        public CriteriaFilter.Builder withSimpleCriteria​(String criteriaKey,
                                                 String criteriaValue)
        Adds the criteriaKey and criteriaValue as a SimpleCriteria to the current criteriaSet. This is a convenience method identical to 
        withSimpleCriteria( new SimpleCriteria(criteriaKey, criteriaValue) );
        Parameters:
        criteriaKey - The key for the SimpleCriteria.
        criteriaValue - The value of the SimpleCriteria.
        Returns:
        this Builder object.

      • newCriteriaSet

        public CriteriaFilter.Builder newCriteriaSet()
        Establishes a new CriteriaSet within this filter. The current criteriaSet is added to the criteriaSetList, and then re-instantiated into a new criteriaSet so that it can contain different criteria.
        Returns:
        this Builder object.

      • newCriteriaSet

        public CriteriaFilter.Builder newCriteriaSet​(String criteriaSetName)
        Establishes a new CriteriaSet within this filter with the given criteriaSetName. The current criteriaSet is added to the criteriaSetList, and then re-instantiated into a new criteriaSet so that it can contain different criteria. The criteriaSetName is then set for the newly instantiated criteriaSet.
        Parameters:
        criteriaSetName - The name for the new criteriaSet.
        Returns:
        this Builder object.

      • build

        public CriteriaFilter build()
        Builds an instance of this CriteriaFilter class, setting the criteriaSetList from this Builder in the CriteriaFilter.
        Returns:
        A CriteriaFilter containing a list of CriteriaSets.
